snippet.textDisplay: I hope you're all doing OK with the unprecedented situation going on. I wish you all to stay safe and healthy, as well your friends and family. It's a good thing we love playing video games at least! This theme is from RO2 before it was rebooted and I'm glad we at least got an awesome soundtrack from Yoko Kanno. I'm not sure about the reboot, but from what I can see it's far from being as good and popular as the first game.

snippet.textDisplay:
Stay safe, Supra! I've been following you since like 2008, when you had one hundred something uploads, and you are the benchmark on youtube for VG OSTs. This crazy time will make us rejoice that we are gamers, and perhaps even make many more discover this awesome hobby of ours. Here's for the next 2400 uploads, and thank you for all the great work!

P.S. such a shame they didn't keep going with this project and changed it to the much inferior Rag 2 we have today :/

snippet.textDisplay: I'll never forget my days in Ragnarok Online (the OG). First mmo experience back in the mid 2000's, I made so many friends, had a blast going to woe on fridays and getting paid like it was a real job xD. Saving money for those head gears and wings I wanted so much, then going to pvp and have a blast too. Wish you are all staying safe! We will get through this!!!
